cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DL 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for relation extraction, specifically hypernymy extraction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses projection learning and word embeddings, which are common techniques in machine learning and deep learning, suggesting that cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. The paper also deals with regularization of the model, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.DL).
